<h3>Sisters Story</h3>
<p>The Sisters Story was also derived from <a href="http://www.splloc.soton.ac.uk/splloc2/lhnt.html">a task developed for the SPLLOC2 project</a>, with slight adaptation.  The main storyline is about two sisters who took a trip together to Spain. The beginning part of the story describes the different kinds of activities that the sisters used to do when they were young to demonstrate their differences which are also apparent in the main events of their trip in Spain.</p>

