<h3>Brothers Story</h3>
<p> This story was created by the LANGSNAP research team. It also followed the same structure, starting with habitual information about the relationship between two brothers (e.g., the different things they would happily do together and things that they would fight about), before the main storyline about what happened when the older brother left for university.  </p>
